;-----------Trooper/rebellion-------------------
INUMBER 935
NAME 233
IFPREVERB READ -1
  IFVAR ITEMBIT0 = 1
    CLEARVERB
    EQUAL ROUNDTIME 40
    ECHO PLAYER To Force Leader Reonna, Commander Veran, Eliditur
    ECHO PLAYER                                                                 
    ECHO PLAYER If you are reading this it means trooper Harris has arrived on andor
    ECHO PLAYER and found you.  I will make this short and to the point.  Recently
    ECHO PLAYER trooper Harris was captured by the Brotherhood during a raid on a
    ECHO PLAYER storage warehouse that the Brotherhood was using to stockpile their
    ECHO PLAYER latest weapons.  The raid was a total failure, they knew when and 
    ECHO PLAYER where we would stride and we lost fourteen good men and women including
    ECHO PLAYER trooper Harris.
    PLREVENT 4
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER We had assumed that all were lost, either dead, to slavery or as experiments for the brotherhood. None has ever been seen again if taken. It was a miracle when Harris showed up three days later at our headquarters, alive and mostly unharmed with a story that is hard to accept.
    PLREVENT 4
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER He was separated from the few prisoners who were taken during the raid and taken away, to where he could not tell us. He was brought before a person who claimed to be a conclave member. This person wanted to meet with a representitive of the resistance to discuss a mutually beneficial arrangement.
    PLREVENT 4
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER I decided to meet with this person, truthfully we expected a ambush that Harris was somehow being used to bring us down, but we felt the benefits of the meeting would be worth the risk. Harris and I met this person two nights after his return in a old abandoned warehouse. We arrived at the appointed time, but nobody was their to meet us, I almost left but decided that we could wait for awhile. Soon after, two people arrive. The conclave person kept his or her identity hidden, his face covered by a black mask and a dark red robe covered the rest but the feeling of power seemed to radiate off of him. The second person was the vile Jonas, and the meeting almost ended with my sword in his chest when he revealed his identity.
    PLREVENT 4
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER The conclave person wishs to make a alliance with us. Apparently a few members of the conclave and certain allies of theirs in the city disapprove of how things are being handled with ysarda and andor. I agreed to pass on the message to my superiors. This seemed to upset him, that I wouldn't make the decision then but he soon agreed to send a message to you and I informed him that if trooper Harris does not return with instructions then I will decide then on our course of action. Trooper Harris carries a message, a device that the conclave member said it could only be activated by a certain person, and if it was taken by our mutual enemies that it would be useless.
    PLREVENT 4
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER I do not trust them, yet to pass up a chance like this? If its true we could get rid of the conclave and the brotherhood within a few months time and turn our efforts to rebuilding out homes. The fight here goes badly, everytime we strike, the enemy is all over us. It's as if they know everything we do, we have not pulled off a successful raid in over three months and our numbers and strength is being slowly eroded away. I estimate that the resistance will collapse within half a year unless something is done and done soon.
    ECHO PLAYER                     
    ECHO PLAYER Respectfully               
    ECHO PLAYER Lieutenant Drake
  ENDIF
ENDIF
NUMBER 3399
NAME Command Center
FIXED_LIGHT
