;-------------------------------------------------------
MNUMBER 134
NAME zharkier
ADJECTIVE 87
AVINE
*DESCRIPTION_START
This hideous version of a zharkier has massive and powerful wings that
stretch out nearly eight feet on each side. Standing at approximately
nine feet tall themsleves, these zharkier are more streamlined and
sleak looking than anything else you've seen. Their eyes pulse with a
dull red glow. It licks its shadowy claws that stretch from its wings
from time to time, eager to sink them into something.
*DESCRIPTION_END
BODY 1200
EXTRABODY 80
ATTACK1 1700
DEFENSE 490
STRATEGY 501
TREASURE 22
IMMUNITY 0 1
IMMUNITY 1 1
IMMUNITY 2 1
IMMUNITY 6 0 
IMMUNITY 5 1
IMMUNITY 3 1
RACE 28
WEAPON 279 -1 50
WEAPONPLUS 3
ARMOR 85
MAGICWEAPON 3
RESIST 250
PSIRESIST 250
NONDISRUPTABLE
SILENCEIGNORE
ALIGNMENT -60
SCRIPTMACRO 86
DISEASE 20 30
FATIGUE 35 45
SPEED 1
MANA 25000
PSI 25000
SPELLUSE 30
SPELL 219
SPELL 519
SPELL 230
SPELLSKILL 1000
CASTLEVEL 99
ALIGNMENT -1
SPECUSE 20
SPECUSES 100
SPECBASE 82
SPECDMG 100
SPECDMGTYPE SLASH
STRENGTH 300
TEXX %s leaps into the air and rakes at %s with the talons on its wings!
TEX1 a winged zharkier extends its wingspan to the fullest and wails loudly.
TEX2 a winged zharkier arches its head back and screeches into the sky.
TEX3 a winged zharkier surrounds its body with its wings, forming a cloak.
TEX4 a winged zharkier's eyes pulse red, as it sees more than you might believe.
TEXE You hear a loud woosh, and a winged zharkier swoops in.
TEXG You hear a loud woosh, and a winged zharkier swoops in.
TEXD crumples to the ground with a skull splitting wail.
TEXA a winged zharkier beats its wings quicker and swoops at
TEXM a winged zharkier hovers for a moment before flying
TEXS a winged zharkier concentrates on the pendant embedded in its chest.
TEXL a winged zharkier focuses its eyes on
TEXZ a winged zharkier slashes furiously at %s with its wings.
  
